Detailed Description

cvmx_npei_ctl_status2

NPEI_CTL_STATUS2 = NPEI's Control Status2 Register

Contains control and status for NPEI. Writes to this register are not ordered with writes/reads to the PCI Memory space. To ensure that a write has completed the user must read the register before making an access(i.e. PCI memory space) that requires the value of this register to be updated.
